name: Albino Style TI
description:
Genral Info

Albino Style was another of my commissioned embeddings and it still is useable on newer models. It tries to replicate a Albino Style Cat Girl, with white hair and red eyes.

Added Example Images with simple prompt from:

  • Kenshi

  • AbyssOrangeMix_nsfw

Usage

To use this embedding you have to download the file aswell as drop it into the "\stable-diffusion-webui\embeddings" folder

To use it in a prompt: "albino_style"

For some models it can be to strong, so use this instead

"(albino_style:0.8)"
